---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';

const lastUpdated = 'May 2026';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`Now: ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="What I'm up to right now." />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Now</h1>
			<p class="updated">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

			<div class="prose">
				<h2>Location</h2>
				<p>East Village, New York City.</p>

				<h2>Work</h2>
				<p>Most recently served as Senior Paid Social Media Director at National Debt Relief until January 2026. Currently providing independent consulting services for high-volume paid social programs, with an active focus on performance creative strategy, attribution modeling, and large-scale media buying operations across Meta and TikTok.</p>

				<h2>Reading</h2>
                                <p>Revisiting existentialist philosophy and theology. Exploring texts that focus on narrative history, behavioral economics, and how humans construct meaning when old centers of gravity shift.</p>

                                <h2>Thinking about</h2>
                                <p><strong>Presence over optimization.</strong> I've spent years researching, building systems, and optimizing outcomes,even attempting to process grief that way. Right now, I'm learning that the best parts of life aren't optimized into existence; they are encountered. I'm focusing on meaning as an accumulation (in a conversation, a meal, a single paragraph) rather than orbiting a single center.</p>

				<h2>Travel</h2>
				<p>Central Europe, April-May 2026. Geneva → Venice → Ljubljana → Graz → Bratislava → Brno → Prague → Wrocław → Dublin.</p>
			</div>

			<p class="note"><em>This is a <a href="https://nownpage.org" target="_blank">/now page</a>. It reflects what I'm actually doing, not what I've done.</em></p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.updated {
		font-size: 0.85em;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		margin-top: -0.5em;
		margin-bottom: 2em;
	}
	.prose h2 {
		font-size: 1.1em;
		margin-top: 1.5em;
		margin-bottom: 0.3em;
	}
	.note {
		margin-top: 3em;
		font-size: 0.85em;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
	}
</style>
